          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>繪師「あやみ」台灣線下展覽「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」，將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/43054\">「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">繪師「あやみ」台灣線下展覽「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」，將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235745/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews01.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews01\" class=\"wp-image-43055\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 2\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235745/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews01.jpg 1000w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235745/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews01-300x150.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235745/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews01-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">繪師「あやみ」繪製了多位VTuber如「花守へるし」、「夜想といき」、「Mint Fantôme」等角色外觀，並同時以VTuber身份經營個人頻道，此次「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」，將在虎之穴台北店舉辦個人原畫展與簽名會。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235749/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02\" class=\"wp-image-43056\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 3\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235749/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235749/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235749/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235749/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews02.jpg 849w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">販售周邊包含一卡通、B2掛軸、3D雙變卡等。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235752/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03\" class=\"wp-image-43057\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 4\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235752/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235752/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235752/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235752/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews03.jpg 849w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235755/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04\" class=\"wp-image-43058\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 5\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235755/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235755/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235755/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235755/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews04.jpg 849w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235758/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05\" class=\"wp-image-43059\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 6\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235758/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235758/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05-212x300.jpg 212w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235758/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235758/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews05.jpg 849w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">另外也會有特製明信片贈送活動（店鋪限定）。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235801/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06-1024x675.jpg\" alt=\"2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06\" class=\"wp-image-43060\" title=\"「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦 7\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235801/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06-1024x675.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235801/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06-300x198.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235801/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06-768x506.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05235801/2025ayamytoranoanatwnews06.jpg 1026w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">消費滿750元，即隨機贈送明信片2張。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">消費滿3,000元，即直接贈送完整一套8款明信片。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">簽名會則預定8月24日舉辦，採抽選資格制，於會場內及台灣虎之穴網路商店購買畫展相關商品每滿1,000元，即可獲贈抽選券乙張。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」，從8月8日－8月24日，在虎之穴台北店舉辦。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">活動資訊</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">舉辦日程：2025年8月8日（五）～8月24日（日）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">營業時間：每日11:00～22:00</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">入場方法：免費 / 會場內【不可】攝影</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※成人限定（未滿18歳者無法入場）</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">會場地址：虎之穴台北店</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">台北市中正區漢口街一段85號 博愛公元大樓2F</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://news.toranoana.jp/324949\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://news.toranoana.jp/324949\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> 新聞資訊頁面</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/43054\">「あやみ展 in TAIWAN」將於8月8日起在虎之穴台北店舉辦</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
