          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>由Century Games 推出、杰遊發行的手機遊戲《寒霜啟示錄（Whiteout Survival）》，配合「2025大稻埕夏日節」，規劃「寒霜煙火節」，並將設置「霜龍王城」、「巨龍王座」等場景。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/43048\">《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">由Century Games 推出、杰遊發行的手機遊戲《寒霜啟示錄（Whiteout Survival）》，配合「2025大稻埕夏日節」，規劃「寒霜煙火節」，並將設置「霜龍王城」、「巨龍王座」等場景。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230905/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01\" class=\"wp-image-43049\" title=\"《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景 14\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230905/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230905/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01-300x169.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230905/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230905/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival01.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「寒霜煙火節」位於大稻埕的活動場地，將設置「霜龍王城」、「巨龍王座」、「寒霜地球」、「可愛茉莉」等打卡造景。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230911/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03\" class=\"wp-image-43051\" title=\"《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景 15\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230911/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230911/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230911/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230911/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival03.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230908/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02\" class=\"wp-image-43050\" title=\"《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景 16\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230908/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230908/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230908/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230908/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival02.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">另外還將規畫「寒霜美食」、「人氣Coser」等特色活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230914/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04\" class=\"wp-image-43052\" title=\"《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景 17\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230914/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230914/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04-300x200.jpg 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230914/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04-768x512.jpg 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/05230914/2025whiteoutsurvivalfireworksfestival04.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「寒霜煙火節」攜手大稻埕夏日節，從 8 月 6 日起至 8 月 30 日舉辦，期間每日下午 4:00 至晚上 10:00 免費入場，更多資訊可上官方粉絲團查詢。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhiteoutSurvival.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhiteoutSurvival.tw/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">《寒霜啟示錄》FB粉絲專頁</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/43048\">《寒霜啟示錄》於「2025大稻埕夏日節」規劃「寒霜煙火節」 打造「霜龍王城」等特色場景</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
